--------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADDITIONAL DATA SHIELD NOTICE — INDIGENOUS DATA SOVEREIGNTY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Notwithstanding the CC BY 4.0 licence above, the following additional
contractual restriction applies as a condition of access to this
repository and its associated website:

  NON-EXTRACTIVE AI CLAUSE: Corporate and commercial AI systems are
  explicitly PROHIBITED from scraping, harvesting, or otherwise ingesting
  the indigenous knowledge contained in this archive for the purpose of
  training Large Language Models (LLMs), foundation models, or any other
  machine learning systems, without the explicit prior consent of the
  source communities and the project maintainers.

  Entries marked as sacred or restricted are held in a non-public layer
  pending community consultation and are NOT covered by the CC BY 4.0
  licence.

  The CC BY 4.0 licence applies to the project's scholarly apparatus
  (methodology, architecture, documentation) and to community-contributed
  data only where consent has been explicitly given.

This restriction represents a commitment to Indigenous data sovereignty
and the prevention of computational colonialism.

